fields.title: Data science with Python
fields.body: Python and data science techniques such as pandas and scikit-learn enable rapid experimentation and analysis.

fields.title: Environmental policy and climate action
fields.body: Environment protection policies require coordinated government efforts and corporate responsibility.

fields.title: Introduction to PostgreSQL full-text search
fields.body: PostgreSQL provides tsvector and tsquery for ranking and boolean search with AND, OR, and NOT operators.

fields.title: Trigram similarity for typo tolerant search
fields.body: The pg_trgm extension enables similarity and the percent operator for fuzzy matching of misspelled terms.

fields.title: Caching strategies with Redis
fields.body: Redis supports caching for frequent queries, lists to store recent queries, and TTL-based invalidation.

fields.title: Network security policies
fields.body: Zero trust and least privilege are key policies in enterprise environments.

fields.title: Python for web development
fields.body: Django provides a batteries-included framework for building secure, maintainable web apps.

fields.title: Deterministic search results
fields.body: Search systems can guarantee deterministic results by avoiding probabilistic models and keeping data in PostgreSQL.

fields.title: Privacy and data governance
fields.body: Strong privacy practices require explicit policies and audit controls.

fields.title: Environment and sustainability
fields.body: Sustainability initiatives rely on accurate measurements of environmental impact over time.

fields.title: Boolean search examples
fields.body: Use AND to require terms, OR to broaden, and NOT to exclude. Parentheses control precedence.

fields.title: PostgreSQL indexes
fields.body: GIN indexes accelerate full-text search; trigram indexes accelerate similarity queries.

fields.title: Python for data engineering
fields.body: Airflow and pandas support ETL pipelines; psycopg integrates Python with Postgres.

fields.title: Operational excellence
fields.body: Health checks, observability, and safe migrations improve reliability.

fields.title: Policies and compliance
fields.body: Security policies should not conflict with productivity; balance is essential.
